English is quickly returned to Whitehall for an emergency meeting with his sequester Bough, a role that Ben Miller reprises.
Now Bough is a married man, tied to the commander of a submarine, an enthusiastic role, in which Vicki Pepperdine is a little underused.
Thus, the Batman and Robin of when things get very ugly in His Majesty's secret service go into action once again and find in Olga Kurylenko the spectacular femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova.
